org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.join

Class JoinEmbeddings

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.join.JoinEmbeddings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PhysicalOperator

    public class JoinEmbeddings
extends Object
implements PhysicalOperator
    Joins two embeddings at given columns and checks for vertex/edge isomorphism/homomorphism. The result is always a new embedding with the following constraints.
    • new entries of the right embedding are always appended to the left embedding
    • duplicate fields are removed, i.e., the join columns are stored once in the result
    • all properties from the right side are appended to the proeprties of the left side, no deduplication is performed
